## Remarks  
 你可以获取用于初始化的识别引擎使用的标识信息<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.RecognizerInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>为<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>对象或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.RecognizerInfo%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>为<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>对象。  
  
 实例中返回的信息<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>从获取<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer>由中设置**语音属性**的成员**控制面板**。  
  
 你可以使用的实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>构造的特定配置<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.%23ctor%28System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo%29>构造函数。  
  
 静态方法<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers%2A>返回的所有可用列表<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>配置中的以<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>实例。  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 以下示例将验证给定<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>和标识符字符串与允许<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>配置，表示为一份<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>对象。  
  
 如果<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>和标识符字符串有效，该示例创建的新实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine>使用<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>作为自变量的实例。  
  
```csharp  
  
private SpeechRecognitionEngine SelectRecognizer(CultureInfo requiredCulture, string requiredId)   
{  
  // Select based on a specific recognizer configuration  
  SpeechRecognitionEngine speechRecognitionEngine=null;  
  foreach (RecognizerInfo config in SpeechRecognitionEngine.InstalledRecognizers())   
  {  
    if (config.Culture.Equals(requiredCulture) && config.Id== requiredId)   
    {  
      speechRecognitionEngine = new SpeechRecognitionEngine(config);  
      break;  
    }  
  }  
  return speechRecognitionEngine;  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 下面的示例实现单击按钮用于显示中的所有信息<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo>对象在<xref:System.Windows.Forms.MessageBox>。  
  
 中包含的键/值对<xref:System.Collections.Generic.IDictionary%602>返回实例<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizerInfo.AdditionalInfo%2A>串联成一个文本表。  
  
```csharp  
private void recognizerInfoButton_Click(object sender, EventArgs e)   
{  
  RecognizerInfo info = _recognizer.RecognizerInfo;  
  string AudioFormats = "";  
  foreach (SpeechAudioFormatInfo fmt in info.SupportedAudioFormats)   
  {  
    AudioFormats += String.Format("       {0}\n", fmt.EncodingFormat.ToString());  
  }  
  string AdditionalInfo = "";  
  foreach (string key in info.AdditionalInfo.Keys)   
  {  
    AdditionalInfo += String.Format("      {0}: {1}\n", key, info.AdditionalInfo[key]);  
  }  
  MessageBox.Show(String.Format(  
                     "Name:                 {0 } \n" +  
                     "Description:          {1} \n" +  
                     "SupportedAudioFormats:\n" +  
                     " {2} " +  
                     "Culture:              {3} \n" +  
                     "AdditionalInfo:       \n" +  
                     " {4}\n",  
                     info.Name.ToString(),  
                     info.Description.ToString(),  
                     AudioFormats,  
                     info.Culture.ToString(),  
                     AdditionalInfo));  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 A<xref:System.Globalization.CultureInfo>对象可以包括区域性、 关联的语言、 国家/地区、 所使用的日历，和如何设置日期和排序字符串的名称。  
  
   
  
